Designed for beginners, families and recreational players

This relatively short course in a sparsely-wooded neighborhood park is designed to be approachable for beginners and those playing with their families. The course has two sets of tee boxes: Blue, shorter and designed for beginners, and Red, slightly longer and designed for recreational and intermediate players.
